shows.title: Salma The Peaceful Human
shows.description: Adopting the philosophy of having no enemies does not mean we allow others to harm or exploit us. Instead, it's about recognizing that every person we encounter is navigating their own life, just as we are. They have their own motivations, desires, fears, and struggles that we may not fully understand

shows.title: Sara and her full storage
shows.description: One day Sara was playing with her phone when suddenly a strange message appeared,"Your storage is full please delete some files" Sara Hurried up and called Fady and told him about her problem but he just laughed and hangs up Sara now can't hear Whatsapp voice messages,Sara decided to hear it on the laptop but she remembered it has viruses on it :( , watch the movie to know what will Sara do
